January 31,2020.

The seventh day of the first lunar month.

Day 9 of the city closure in Wuhan.

The Gate of Heaven was sealed for the eighth day.

In the early morning, the World Health Organization (WHO) held a press conference to inform the World: China's new pneumonia epidemic constitutes a public health emergency of international concern (PHEIC) . "We must remember that these are people, not numbers, " the WHO official added, recalling a similar quote by Takeshi Kitano after the Japanese 2011 Thoku earthquake and tsunami: "A disaster is not the death of 20,000 people, but the death of one person, 20,000 times. "

One The Sun Also Rises, a wild boar was running wild on the second ring road in Wuhan in the middle of the night.
